remarks.code:
public class MyJob : TraceStaxPeriodicBackgroundService
{
    public MyJob(TraceStaxClient client)
        : base(client, interval: TimeSpan.FromMinutes(5)) { }

    protected override string JobName  => "MyJob";
    protected override string QueueName => "default";

    protected override async Task ExecuteJobAsync(CancellationToken ct)
    {
        // do work …
    }
}

member.remarks:
Register during application startup, after building the bus:

busControl.ConnectConsumeObserver(new TraceStaxConsumeObserver(client));

Or use the convenience extension method:

busControl.AddTraceStax(client);

example.code:
var busControl = Bus.Factory.CreateUsingRabbitMq(cfg => { ... });
busControl.AddTraceStax(tracestaxClient);
await busControl.StartAsync();
